Elisabeth Röhm https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Elisabeth_R%C3%B6hm 0 Elisabeth Röhm (, German: [eˈliːzabɛt ˈʁøːm]; born April 28, 1973) is a German-American television and film actress. She is best known for playing Assistant District Attorney Serena Southerlyn in the American TV series Law Order and Detective Kate Lockley in the TV series Angel, and for her work with David O.
